{"tid":2220964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"還押7個月 非暴動案件手足被胡雅文裁判官判刑3年10個月","createTime":"2020-09-28T04:39:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T04:47:09.000Z","uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6b3f7089eba67a5afcd0cef85c5c5051362b515d","tid":2220964,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"#區域法院第廿七庭<br />\n#胡雅文法官<br />\n#20200129葵涌<br />\n#判刑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳(17)🛑已還押逾7個月<br />\n<br />\n控罪：1.企圖縱火<br />\n           2.管有物品意圖損壞財產<br />\n<br />\n案情： 被指於2020年1月29日在葵涌警署近停車場閘入口，連同兩名身份不詳的人，無合法辯解而用火損壞屬於香港警務處的葵涌警署。管有玻璃瓶內有腐蝕性液體，高濃度硫酸，可對皮膚造成嚴重傷害，另管有載有白電油的玻璃樽，在警誡下承認投擲汽油彈，另承認在某大廈內的27個汽油彈、1個打火機燃料、2枝通渠水及3個空玻璃樽為製作汽油彈的用剩<br />\n<br />\n判刑：3年10個月<br />\n<br />\nTG: 法庭文字直播台<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=bb9ec38c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live</a>"},{"pid":"5a5302091afe81f76ac2161e4fea36996e0dd88e","tid":2220964,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e685c2660f615206d6e06d0a3e5b7ea61ee01b","tid":2220964,"uid":157862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"憑咩判人坐監"},{"pid":"e5b3639b4ac9c911a19f85a7d8cb99c3568288c1","tid":2220964,"uid":78703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32e685c2660f615206d6e06d0a3e5b7ea61ee01b","tid":2220964,"uid":157862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:44:27.000Z","msg":"憑咩判人坐監"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:45:05.000Z","msg":"手足認左罪"},{"pid":"2bf52ac2fda3dec7bc455b606e393fbac9300cf0","tid":2220964,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T04:47:09.000Z"